title: Hamster Ball Gold + Unlock all levels - Hellonagol
description:
Take control of your Hamster and go a-rollin' through the craziest obstacle course you've ever seen...
It's rowdy rolling rodent racing! Take control of your Hamster and go a-rollin' through the craziest obstacle course you've ever seen! But be careful, because the clock is ticking and everything is out to stop you! Roll, roll, roll your wheel...!!!

Here are some key features of "Hamsterball":

- Fifteen unique race courses, at three skill levels!
- Multiplayer races and party games!
- Amazing musical sountrack!
- Play with mouse, joystick, keyboard, or trackball!


To unlock all levels open All Levels.reg found in the Hamsterball folder.
